                </div>

                <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 text-white">
                    Acute injury? Get fast help.
                </h1>
                <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-sky-100 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                    We've made it easy for both you and your healthcare provider to submit a referral digitally – you'll often get an appointment within 24 hours.
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 space-y-16">

            <section>
                <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl overflow-hidden max-w-5xl mx-auto">
                    <div class="px-6 py-10 md:p-12 lg:p-16">
                        
                        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 mb-8">
                            How to seek urgent care with us – no matter where you live
                        </h2>

                        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">

                            <div>
                                <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-4">
                                    The easiest way to get urgent care with us is to have a healthcare provider send a referral directly to us.
                                </p>
                                
                                <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
                                    We are connected to the National Patient Overview (NPÖ), which gives us access to your <strong>digital medical records</strong>. Additionally, we have connections to radiology systems <strong>throughout Sweden</strong> and can, with your consent, <strong>quickly retrieve your digital X-rays</strong>, regardless of region.
                                </p>
                                
                                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Ask your healthcare provider to refer you:</h3>
                                <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-lg text-gray-600">
                                    <li>Your doctor at an urgent care clinic or health center</li>
                                    <li>Digital healthcare provider (e.g., Kry)</li>
                                    <li>Your physiotherapist</li>
                                    <li>Your naprapath or chiropractor</li>
                                    <li>Registered Nurse</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>

                            <div class="space-y-6">
                                
                                <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-blue-200">
                                    <p class="text-lg text-blue-900 font-semibold">
                                        Have you received a paper referral?
                                    </p>
                                    <p class="mt-2 text-gray-700">
                                        Instead of waiting for processing in your home region, you can photograph and submit the referral directly to our medical records system. Use the digital referral upload in the section below.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                                
                                <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-blue-500">
                                    <div class="flex">
                                        <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                                            <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-blue-500" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                                                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-7-4a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zM9 9a1 1 0 000 2v3a1 1 0 001 1h1a1 1 0 100-2v-3a1 1 0 00-1-1H9z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                                            </svg>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="ml-3">
                                            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-blue-900">Important information about X-rays</h3>
                                            <p class="mt-2 text-blue-800">
                                                We <strong>prefer</strong> that your injured shoulder, elbow or knee is <strong>X-rayed</strong> before your visit, but it is <strong>not an absolute requirement</strong>.
                                            </p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                
                            </div>

                        </div> 
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section id="info-vardgivare">
                <div class="text-center mb-12">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-center text-sky-700">
                        Digital Referral Upload: Two Ways In
                    </h2>
                    <p class="mt-4 text-xl text-gray-500 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                        Whether you're a patient or healthcare provider, on desktop or mobile, here are the ways to upload your referral:
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                    
                    <!-- COLUMN 1: DESKTOP -->
                    <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg flex flex-col transition duration-300 hover:shadow-xl">
                        
                        <!-- Header: Text Left, Icon Right -->
                        <div class="flex flex-row justify-between items-start mb-6">
                            <div class="mr-4">
                                <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Upload from Desktop (PC/Mac)</h3>
                                <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">
                                    The easiest method for healthcare providers at a clinic.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                            <!-- SVG: Desktop icon -->
                            <svg class="w-16 h-16 flex-shrink-0 text-sky-700 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                                <path d="M8,2h8a2,2,0,0,1,2,2V20a2,2,0,0,1-2,2H8a2,2,0,0,1-2-2V4A2,2,0,0,1,8,2M8,4V6h8V4H8m8,4H8v2h8V8m0,10H14v2h2Z"/>
                                <rect width="24" height="24" fill="none"/>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="flex-grow mb-8">
                            <ol class="list-decimal list-inside text-lg text-gray-700 space-y-2">
                                <li>Copy the password</li>
                                <li>Click on referral upload.</li>
                                <li>Authenticate with BankID.</li>
                                <li>Upload referral (PDF, image file or media).</li>
                            </ol>
                            
                            <div class="mt-6 p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-gray-400">
                                <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Why only these file types?</p>
                                <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-700">
                                    To protect your patient data, we only accept files such as PDF, images, photos (JPG, PNG) and video (MP4). These formats cannot contain malicious code, ensuring secure transfer and GDPR compliance.
                                </p>
                                <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-700 font-medium">
                                    Files with editable text (e.g., from word processors) are not accepted.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Password box -->
                        <div class="mb-6 bg-sky-100 border-4 border-sky-700 rounded-2xl p-6 text-center">
                            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-sky-900 mb-3 uppercase tracking-wide">Password</p>
                            <code 
                                class="block text-5xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-sky-700 tracking-wider select-all cursor-text font-mono"
                                style="user-select: all; -webkit-user-select: all; -moz-user-select: all;"
                            >
                                2026nyår
                            </code>
                            <p class="text-xs text-sky-600 mt-3">
                                Double-click to select → Copy (Ctrl+C) → Click "Start Referral Upload"
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        
                        <a href="https://web1.storegate.com/share/M85ZWN0" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-block w-full bg-sky-700 text-white font-bold py-4 px-6 rounded-full shadow-lg hover:bg-sky-800 transition duration-300 text-lg text-center">
                            Start Referral Upload
                        </a>
                    </div>

                    <!-- COLUMN 2: MOBILE -->
                    <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg flex flex-col transition duration-300 hover:shadow-xl">
                        
                        <!-- Header: Text Left, Icon Right -->
                        <div class="flex flex-row justify-between items-start mb-6">
                            <div class="mr-4">
                                <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Upload from Mobile (Patient & Provider on the go)</h3>
                                <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">
                                    Perfect for patients with paper referrals or healthcare providers away from the office (e.g., on the ski slope, in the countryside).
                                </p>
                            </div>
                            <!-- SVG: Mobile icon -->
                            <svg class="w-16 h-16 flex-shrink-0 text-sky-700" viewBox="0 0 128 128" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                                <!-- Mobile body (dark blue outline, rounded corners) -->
                                <rect x="34" y="14" width="60" height="100" rx="12" ry="12" 
                                      fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="6"/>
                                <!-- Screen (inner rectangle) -->
                                <rect x="40" y="24" width="48" height="68" rx="6" ry="6" 
                                      fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="4"/>
                                <!-- Home button / fingerprint reader at bottom -->
                                <circle cx="64" cy="102" r="6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="4"/>
                                <!-- Speaker/earpiece at top -->
                                <rect x="54" y="20" width="20" height="4" rx="2" ry="2" 
                                      fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"/>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="flex-grow mb-8">
                            <ol class="list-decimal list-inside text-lg text-gray-700 space-y-3">
                                <li>Copy the password</li>
                                <li>Click on referral upload</li>
                                <li>Log in with BankID.</li>
                                <li>
                                    Upload your file. You can either:
                                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-6 mt-2 space-y-2 text-base">
                                        <li><strong>Photograph</strong> your paper referral directly.</li>
                                        <li>Upload a <strong>screenshot</strong> or existing file.</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </li>
                            </ol>
                            
                            <div class="mt-6 p-4 bg-amber-50 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-amber-500">
                                <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">IMPORTANT (for healthcare providers):</p>
                                <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-700">If you're sending a screenshot of a note, make sure it includes:</p>
                                <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-5 mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm text-gray-700">
                                    <li>Patient's personal identity number</li>
                                    <li>Patient's mobile number</li>
                                    <li>Your name and title</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Password box -->
                        <div class="mb-6 bg-sky-100 border-4 border-sky-700 rounded-2xl p-6 text-center">
                            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-sky-900 mb-3 uppercase tracking-wide">Password</p>
                            <code 
                                class="block text-5xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-sky-700 tracking-wider select-all cursor-text font-mono"
                                style="user-select: all; -webkit-user-select: all; -moz-user-select: all;"
                            >
                                2026nyår
                            </code>
                            <p class="text-xs text-sky-600 mt-3">
                                Double-click to select → Copy (Ctrl+C) → Paste on Storegate page
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        
                        <a href="https://web1.storegate.com/share/M85ZWN0" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-block w-full bg-sky-700 text-white font-bold py-4 px-6 rounded-full shadow-lg hover:bg-sky-800 transition duration-300 text-lg text-center">
                            Start Referral Upload
                        </a>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </section>

            <section>
                <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-8">

                    <!-- START: Infographic section -->
                    <div class="p-8 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl">
                        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-sky-700 mb-8">What happens after your upload?</h2>
                        
                        <!-- Timeline infographic -->
                        <ol class="relative border-l border-gray-300 ml-6">
                            
                            <!-- Step 1 -->
                            <li class="mb-10 ml-6">
                                <!-- Icon/Number dot -->
                                <span class="absolute flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 bg-sky-100 rounded-full -left-4 ring-8 ring-white">
                                    <span class="font-bold text-sky-700">1</span>
                                </span>
                                <!-- Content -->
                                <h3 class="flex items-center mb-1 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
                                    Nurse reviews 
                                    <span class="bg-sky-100 text-sky-800 text-sm font-medium mr-2 px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded ml-3">Morning</span>
                                </h3>
                                <p class="text-base font-normal text-gray-600">A nurse checks your referral and verifies that all details (personal ID number, name, mobile number) are correct. This usually happens in the morning (weekdays).</p>
                            </li>
                            
                            <!-- Step 2 -->
                            <li class="mb-10 ml-6">
                                <span class="absolute flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 bg-sky-100 rounded-full -left-4 ring-8 ring-white">
                                    <span class="font-bold text-sky-700">2</span>
                                </span>
                                <!-- Content -->
                                <h3 class="flex items-center mb-1 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
                                    Specialist evaluates 
                                    <span class="bg-sky-100 text-sky-800 text-sm font-medium mr-2 px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded ml-3">Afternoon</span>
                                </h3>
                                <p class="text-base font-normal text-gray-600">An orthopedic specialist medically evaluates your injury.</p>
                            </li>
                            
                            <!-- Step 3 -->
                            <li class="mb-10 ml-6">
                                <span class="absolute flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 bg-green-100 rounded-full -left-4 ring-8 ring-white">
                                    <!-- Check icon -->
                                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-green-700" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                                        <path d="M10 0a10 10 0 1 0 10 10A10 10 0 0 0 10 0Zm3.7 7.7a1 1 0 0 1 0 1.4l-5 5a1 1 0 0 1-1.4 0l-2-2a1 1 0 1 1 1.4-1.4L8 12.6l4.3-4.3a1 1 0 0 1 1.4 0Z"/>
                                    </svg>
                                </span>
                                <h3 class="mb-1 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">You receive a booking SMS</h3>
                                <p class="text-base font-normal text-gray-600">Once your referral is approved, you'll receive an SMS with a link to book your appointment.</p>
                            </li>
                            
                            <!-- Step 4 -->
                            <li class="ml-6"> <!-- No mb-10 on last item -->
                                <span class="absolute flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 bg-red-100 rounded-full -left-4 ring-8 ring-white">
                                    <!-- Exclamation icon -->
                                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-red-700" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                                        <path d="M10 0a10 10 0 1 0 10 10A10 10 0 0 0 10 0Zm0 16a1 1 0 1 1 0-2 1 1 0 0 1 0 2Zm0-12a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v6a1 1 0 1 1-2 0V5a1 1 0 0 1 1-1Z"/>
                                    </svg>
                                </span>
                                <h3 class="mb-1 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">IMPORTANT: Complete the questionnaire</h3>
                                <p class="text-base font-normal text-gray-600">After booking your appointment, you will be directed to a digital questionnaire about your injury and health. <strong class="text-gray-900">It is essential that you complete this</strong> so we can prepare for your visit.</p>
                            </li>
                        </ol>
                        
                    </div>
                    <!-- END: Infographic section -->

                    <div class="p-6 bg-amber-50 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-amber-500">
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Need an appointment extra quickly?</h3>
                        <p class="mt-2 text-gray-700 text-lg">
                            Some acute injuries are time-critical. If you or your healthcare provider determine that you need to be seen immediately, <strong class="text-gray-900">call us directly</strong> after uploading your referral. We often have the ability to schedule extra appointments after 4:00 PM for these cases.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </section>
            </div> 
    </main>


</BaseLayout>

